==In popular culture==
Motion pictures that have been shot in Highland Park include:

* &quot;Reservoir Dogs&quot;
* &quot;The Lincoln Lawyer&quot; â location for the bar The York on York
* &quot;Gangster Squad&quot; â In early 2012 the entire Highland Park downtown area along Figueroa Street was redone to look like post-WWII-era Los Angeles for the film. 
* &quot;Yes Man&quot; 
* &quot;Cyrus&quot;
* &quot;Tuff Turf&quot;

Television and feature films have used the old Los Angeles Police Department building in the 6000 block of York Boulevard.

Smith Estate, an historic hilltop Victorian house, has been a shooting location for horror films such as &quot;Spider Baby&quot;, &quot;Silent Scream&quot; and &quot;&quot;.

